{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Design
    
    Add a centered heading: “AI that knows your skin”
    
    Add a subheading: “From scans to routines – precision care in one mirror.”
    
    Show a 3-column grid of tall image cards with rounded corners.
    
    Each card includes:
    
    a translucent pill label top-left (editable text)
    
    a circular plus button top-right (visual only)
    
    a large headline bottom-left (editable, 2–3 lines)
    
    optional small caption under the headline
    
    Interaction (use Shopify native components, no JS)
    
    Under the grid, add a Collapsible content / Collapsible rows area (accordion).
    
    Each accordion row corresponds to one card.
    
    Row header includes the same headline and a plus icon.
    
    When a row is opened, show a two-column layout:
    
    left: the card image
    
    right: title, paragraph text, and a bullet list
    
    Ensure only one row is open at a time (accordion behavior).
    
    Theme editor structure
    
    Use blocks: each feature is one block with: image, pill label, headline, caption, detail title, detail paragraph, bullet list.
    
    Section settings: max width, padding, corner radius.
    
    Responsive
    
    Mobile: cards become 1 column; accordion detail layout stacks image above text.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-skin-features-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
